course.subject: MATH
course.name: Interest Rate Models
course.description: Theory of interest rates, yield curves, short rates, forward rates.  Short rate models: Vasicek model and Cox-Ingersoll-Ross models.  Term structure models: Hull-White fitting procedure.  Heath-Jarrow-Morton pricing framework.  LIBOR and swap market models, Brace-Gatarek-Musiela approach.  Affine models.
